    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Raju bhai is a new don in town. He enjoys hanging people every weekend.\n\tThis weekend he assembled N people in a circular manner (1,2,..N,1) and choosen a random integer K. \n\tHe framed certain rules to hang people.\n\t\n<p>\tRule 1: He skips K-1 persons (inclusive) and hang Kth person.</p>\n<p>\tRule 2: He always starts counting from 1st person.</p>\n<p>\tRule 3: The last person will be allowed to live for rest of his life.</p>\n<p>\u00a0Save our friend Mary by choosing correct position in the initial circle.\n\t<p>You have to return the integer x, such that if mary is positioned at x in [1..N] she</p>\n\twill not be killed, if no such position exists, return -1</p>\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>Input description.</p>\n<li>The first line of the input contains an integer T denoting the number of test cases.</li>\n<li>The description of T test cases follows.</li>\n<li>Each test case contains integer N denoting number of persons</li>\n<li>Followed by  integer k denoting the integer choosen by Rajubhai</li>\n<ul>\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>Output description.</p>\n<ul>\n <li>Output the position, such that if mary is positioned at that position in [1..N] she will not be killed.</li>\n <li>if no such position exists, return -1</li>\n\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>T</b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>3</sup></b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>3</sup></b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>k</b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>4</sup></b></li>\n\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n1\n5\n2\n<b>Output:</b>\n3\n</pre>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Explanation</h3>\n<p><pre>Given N=5, K=2\n\t    Initial state: 1,2,3,4,5\n\tStep 1: skips 1 and hangs 2\n\t\t1,3,4,5\n\tStep 2: Now skips 3 and hangs 4\n\t\t1,3,5\n\tStep 3: Now skips 5 and hangs 1\n\t\t3,5\n\tStep 4: Now skips 3 and hangs 5\n\t\t3\n\tAs 3 is only person, he lets him live..</pre> </p>",
